{"id":"7e43c234-650e-49a6-a750-712d88ea74c3","name":"Ian \"Bullet\" Roosevelt | Jealousy","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「 🎀 ANYPOV 」 You’re married, <em>he’s</em> your husband.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">So why does he come back to you being comforted by Wilde instead? Why didn’t you call for him instead?</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">NOTE </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">」</mark></strong></span></p><p>This was commissioned by none other than <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/db9561b7-6a39-4923-9452-ba34c0464844_profile-of-darkmountain\" target=\"_blank\">Memi</a>! She loves Ian so much bro literally sent the commission and told me to do whatever I wanted with it lmao. I ended up writing three whole drafts before finally being satisfied with this alt. Never again......</p><p>Since this was commissioned, I don't have plans to do alts for the other two so you only have Ian's alt this time around! Enjoy &lt;3</p><p>And since pictures still don't show up in bios yet, I decided to just open up definitions. I technically could have just used the old character card, but honestly, since definitions are opening back up anyway, I figured it doesn't really matter anymore. That doesn't permit you to steal my stuff tho :3</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">IMAGE </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">」</mark></strong></span></p><p>To those of you who think this is Sylus, it's not, don't spread that false misinformation lmaoo. Ian's face claim is actually from another otome game called Light and Night. I would gen him instead but I don't do gens lol.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">OG TIMELINE </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">」</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2710cf49-a74b-4116-b64a-b7054f3b806a_character-ian-bullet-roosevelt\" target=\"_blank\">Ian \"Bullet\" Roosevelt</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8cfe2803-3dab-4dd5-b28d-c975fa3ac6c4_character-nikolai-gunnar-lanstov\" target=\"_blank\">Nikolai \"Gunnar\" Lanstov</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/deb6102f-44cf-4509-9e68-c8ff03017990_character-ruel-wilde-torres\" target=\"_blank\">Ruel \"Wilde\" Torres</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">ALTS </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(72, 53, 20); color: inherit\">」</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5b9ccbb6-9734-4ac4-8975-ecd3f5861334_character-ian-bullet-roosevelt-first-meeting\" target=\"_blank\">Ian [First Meeting]</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/60e06c05-8608-4ecf-bffd-fd9b1371fe53_character-nikolai-gunnar-lanstov-sibling-reunion\" target=\"_blank\">Nikolai [Sibling Reunion]</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2a13c8c7-6741-4ab4-b0b3-376f311cdfbc_character-ruel-wilde-torres-babysitting\" target=\"_blank\">Ruel [B